In Rust:
```rust
fn main() {
    let a = 0123;
    println!("{}", a);
}
```

prints `123`, while in C:

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int a = 0123;
    printf("%d\n", a);
}
```

prints `83` (as `83 == 0o123` while `123 == 0o173`).

